    },
    {
      "id": "e1832dbf-775a-4264-a96a-eb4a98c19f0b",
      "content": "USER: Looking back at this year, what did I actually learn? Help me figure that out. ASSISTANT: Let's map it. What did you try this year that scared you? What did you avoid and why? What did you finish that surprised you? Who did you help? What do you know about yourself at 23 that you didn't know at 22? Answers to those usually reveal the real learning underneath the events. Take a pass at one and I'll help you dig deeper.",
      "memory_type": "private_ai_chat",
